<div id="nodeDecoration"><h1 id="nodeTitle">7.2. Lumbalgias Y Problemas Lumbares</h1></div>
<div class="iDevice_wrapper FreeTextIdevice" id="id212">
<div class="iDevice emphasis0">
<div id="ta212_85" class="block iDevice_content">

